<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 12 Jun 2026 02:14:37 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>班克曼-弗里德的赦免重新开启了痛苦的加密记忆</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-06-11/bankman-fried-s-pardon-bid-reopens-painful-crypto-memories</link><description>对于许多加密货币领域的长期参与者来说，SBF 的要求令人恼火。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iqF8f6pRIaYw/v4/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jun 2026 21:00:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-06-11/bankman-fried-s-pardon-bid-reopens-painful-crypto-memories</guid></item><item><title>SpaceX 加密货币交易员押注 2.2 万亿美元估值</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-11/spacex-crypto-traders-are-betting-on-a-2-2-trillion-valuation</link><description>加密货币交易员正在忽略 SpaceX 的预期 IPO 价格，并在埃隆·马斯克 (Elon Musk) 的火箭、卫星和人工智能公司上市前给予其更高的估值。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iKgq4ftSvO2c/v3/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jun 2026 14:12:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-11/spacex-crypto-traders-are-betting-on-a-2-2-trillion-valuation</guid></item><item><title>匈牙利将与欧尔班相反，将加密货币交易合法化</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-11/hungary-to-decriminalize-crypto-trading-in-reversal-from-orban</link><description>匈牙利将取消加密货币交易的刑罪化，扭转前领导人欧尔班·维克托 (Viktor Orban) 实行的限制。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iCZl6IiYg2Rs/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jun 2026 10:05:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-11/hungary-to-decriminalize-crypto-trading-in-reversal-from-orban</guid></item><item><title>安德森霍洛维茨支持华尔街巨头使用的区块链</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-11/andreessen-horowitz-backs-blockchain-used-by-wall-street-giants</link><description>随着华尔街加速关注使用加密货币背后的技术来处理传统资产，区块链建设者 Digital Asset Holdings LLC 在由 Andreessen Horowitz 的主要加密货币基金领投的新一轮融资中筹集了 3.55 亿美元。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iikbQ6yPtjn4/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jun 2026 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-11/andreessen-horowitz-backs-blockchain-used-by-wall-street-giants</guid></item><item><title>日本采取类似股票监管方式来监管加密货币以推动市场增长</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-11/japan-moves-to-regulate-crypto-like-stocks-in-market-growth-push</link><description>日本议会准备通过立法，将加密货币纳入与股票相同的监管框架下，此举旨在扩大数字资产的获取范围。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i8rO5LTKUbio/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jun 2026 06:14:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-11/japan-moves-to-regulate-crypto-like-stocks-in-market-growth-push</guid></item><item><title>比特币抛售导致一半供应交易亏损</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-10/bitcoin-selloff-leaves-half-of-all-supply-trading-at-a-loss</link><description>比特币最近的下跌是如此严重，以至于其流通供应量的一半以上陷入亏损。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ixLMZOS84aTQ/v3/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jun 2026 11:05:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-10/bitcoin-selloff-leaves-half-of-all-supply-trading-at-a-loss</guid></item></channel></rss>